---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="Turf Tech HQ affiliate disclosure — learn how we use affiliate links and how they affect our content recommendations.">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2 font-heading">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 14, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-text">
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-6">
          Turf Tech HQ ("we," "us," or "our") believes in full transparency with our readers. This page explains our use of affiliate links and how they may affect you.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">What Are Affiliate Links?</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Some links on turftechhq.com are affiliate links. This means that if you click a link and make a purchase, we may earn a small commission — at no additional cost to you. The price you pay is exactly the same whether you use our link or go directly to the retailer.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Amazon Associates Program</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Turf Tech HQ is a participant in the <strong>Amazon Services LLC Associates Program</strong>, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          When you click an Amazon affiliate link on our site and complete a purchase, we earn a commission. This helps us keep the site free and continue producing quality landscaping content.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Editorial Independence</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Our editorial content is <strong>never influenced by affiliate relationships</strong>. We only recommend products and services we genuinely believe are useful to our readers. Affiliate commissions do not determine which products appear in our articles, nor do they affect our ratings or opinions.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>We research products independently before recommending them.</li>
          <li>We do not accept payment for positive reviews.</li>
          <li>We are not paid to feature specific products in our content.</li>
          <li>Affiliate links are included only for products we would recommend regardless of commission.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">FTC Compliance</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          In accordance with the <strong>U.S. Federal Trade Commission (FTC) guidelines</strong> on endorsements and testimonials, we disclose our affiliate relationships clearly and prominently. This page, along with in-content disclosures where appropriate, satisfies that requirement.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Questions?</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships or how we select products to recommend, please reach out through our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary-light hover:underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Turf Tech HQ</strong><br />
          <a href="/contact" class="text-primary-light hover:underline">turftechhq.com/contact</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
